g.text: Shows the three main components (Lexer, Parser, Evaluator) and their data flow: Input String → Tokens → AST → Number. Also shows the Environment (symbol table) interacting with the Evaluator.

div.p: Tokens Stream of lexical units (numbers, operators, parentheses)
Parser Builds AST according to operator precedence and associativity rules
Abstract Syntax Tree Hierarchical representation of expression structure
Evaluator Recursively evaluates AST nodes to compute final result
